" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hjGZqJ dfjDDX pf-57_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-jIkXHa bGnPis pf-58_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-iqVWFU kwUChp pf-60_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-61_ pf-text-1">The CQC regulates over 30,000 health and social care providers in England alone, including hospitals and GP surgeries, care homes, and home-care agencies.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-63_ pf-text-1">According to the CQC's 2020/21 State of Care report, 87% of healthcare providers and 77% of adult social care services were rated as 'good' or 'outstanding' in terms of overall quality.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-65_ pf-text-1">In 2019/20, the CQC carried out over 22,000 inspections across various health and social care settings, highlighting the scale and scope of its regulatory activities.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-pVTFL cZzoXH pf-67_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hjGZqJ dfjDDX pf-68_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-jIkXHa bGnPis pf-69_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key definitions</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-iqVWFU kwUChp pf-71_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-72_ pf-text-1"><strong>Care Quality Commission (CQC)</strong> - The independent regulator of health and social care services in England, responsible for assessing and rating providers based on standards of safety, quality, and effectiveness.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-74_ pf-text-1"><strong>Regulation</strong> - The process of monitoring, overseeing, and enforcing compliance with regulatory standards and requirements set by the CQC.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-76_ pf-text-1"><strong>Compliance</strong> - Adherence to statutory regulations, guidelines, and best practices to ensure the delivery of safe, high-quality care.</li></ul></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hjGZqJ dfjDDX pf-78_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Care_Quality_Commission_Compliance_ComplyPlus_for_Healthcare_Regulation_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1711616109" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Care_Quality_Commission_Compliance_ComplyPlus_for_Healthcare_Regulation_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1711616109 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Care_Quality_Commission_Compliance_ComplyPlus_for_Healthcare_Regulation_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_1000x.jpg?v=1711616109 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Care_Quality_Commission_Compliance_ComplyPlus_for_Healthcare_Regulation_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_500x.jpg?v=1711616109 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Navigating Care Quality Commission Compliance ComplyPlus™ for Healthcare Regulation - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Navigating Care Quality Commission Compliance ComplyPlus™ for Healthcare Regulation - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-kYHfwS QlfnY pf-79_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-ZOtfp cLnRKw pf-80_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by&nbsp;monkeybusiness&nbsp;via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pVTFL cZzoXH pf-82_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class